---
title: Crispy Shallot Crumbed Pork with Garlic Soy Veggies & Sesame Dressing
description: This crumbed delight is a few steps above your usual pub grub! With a golden crispy shallot and panko coating, a bed of fluffy jasmine rice, garlic veggies and nutty sesame dressing, this fantastic fusion is sure to become a new certified favourite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crispy-shallot-crumbed-pork-db8ac5bf.jpg
